  <summary>Cross-platform Mouse and Keyboard Macro Automation Tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      CrossMacro is a powerful cross-platform mouse and keyboard macro recording and playback tool.
      It supports recording inputs, text expansion, and playing them back with adjustable speed and looping.
      Works on Linux (Wayland - X11) and Windows.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Record and replay mouse movements, clicks, and keyboard events</li>
      <li>Text Expansion support for productivity</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support (Linux Wayland/X11, Windows)</li>
      <li>Global hotkeys for control</li>
      <li>Adjustable playback speed and loop mode</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
